subject: United States Open (Golf)
lead_paragraph: Michelle Wie, 17, who vowed to try again this year after failing to qualify for the 2006 United States Open, was not among the 8,544 golfers to submit qualifying applications for this year’s tournament, according to the United States Golf Association.
